/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01c5fde83a4dfd351ab6474b6ed3678911a9aab","tid":310546,"uid":61210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:33:38.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"896bbddd323ff5bf45ea1863635d2bb96f257a9d","tid":310546,"uid":67424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:12:56.000Z","msg":"其實消委會測試產品後會點處置堆物件？🤔<br />\n<br />\n捐？退？"},{"pid":"6e25c7e2c54de3595b111b92cb74eee78ec2d73d","tid":310546,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T09:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7e9a6e81262bd8f6dbcd3ce81c2202fdfd49a4","tid":310546,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T09:42:13.000Z","msg":"其實消委會大唔大洗關我鬼事咩，最重要係D測試準唔準，同埋多D權力打擊黑店"},{"pid":"f6f5a02f2e86e372976c4902defa29226e308f4a","tid":310546,"uid":25100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T09:46:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實消委會大唔大洗關我鬼事咩，最重要係D測試準唔準，同埋多D權力打擊黑店</blockquote><br />\nOn9"}]}